19/12/2003
RIJEKA, Croatia -- Local police in Rijeka reported the arrest of around 50 people suspected of drug smuggling in the area Thursday (18 December).
Police searched around 20 apartments used by the suspects and seized various types of narcotics prepared for sale.
Investigators believe those detained have been working in a well-organised network with connections elsewhere in Croatia and abroad.
(HINA, HRT - 18/12/03)
